inn1.comm: good channel from Harris and we see some nice swing away from McCullum as he pushes at the line but misses
good shape again but a fraction shorter and McCullum guides it down to third man to get underway
back of a length and Ingram is back and pushing into the off side for a quick single. Harris moves sharply to his left but can't prevent the single
full and it swings away and McCullum drives off the outside half of the bat to Voges at point wo dives and misfields to allow the single
back of a length and straight and Ingram stands tall and pulls in front of square leg for four
cracking delivery from Harris, he hits a good length and Ingram plays without intent and edges through to Haddin who takes the simplest of catches. Great start for Australia
good length and angled across McCullum who leaves it alone
good length, a fraction too much width, McCullum is back and driving off the back foot over where third slip would be and races away for four, beating third man
McCullum advances and Bollinger angles the ball straight across him and he leaves it alone
slightly fuller and McCullum moves forward and punches through straight mid wicket for a couple, good timing
back of a length and McCullum moves back and defends powerfully back past the bowler
good length again and angled across McCullum who is content on leaving. No movement for Bollinger but he's still smiling
great start to Guptill, Harris hits a perfect length and gets Guptill to play as he defends back to the bowler
angled into the pads and Guptill is underway playing to fine leg
back of a length and McCullum trie to flick it off his hip but misses and it takes him on the thigh
good length forces McCullum back and he pushes into the covers nicely for a single
Harris continues to hit a good length and Guptill is in behind it solidly and defending into the off side
Harris oversteps this time, hits a good channel and Guptill is back and defending
Guptill moves back in the crease and Harris tries to hit the hole but offers width and Guptill crunches him through the covers for four
back of a length and McCullum is back and defending neatly into the off side
good length on off stump and McCullum plays back down the pitch
decent length but McCullum is onto it in a flash and pulls over square leg for four. McCullum is just so quick on his feet and his hands are even quicker through the ball
slightly fuller and McCullum tries to overhit it through the covers but mistimes it and can only get one
fullish length and Guptill is half forward and defending awkwardly into the covers
good delivery outside off and Guptill pushes into the off side and calls wait, before Hussey charges to his right at point and dives to collect the ball in one hand
McCullum advances and crashes it to point where Hussey parries it to Voges and there is no run
back of a length angled into middle stump and McCullum woorks it into mid wicket and they take a couple. Well run by this electric pair
Harris oversteps again and McCullum square drives through the hand of Voges at point to third man. Another free-hit coming up
length ball and Guptill heaves it into the leg side but without any timing and straight to deep square leg
uses his feet and drives on the up past mid off for four
good reply as Harris hits the hole perfectly and McCullum digs it out
back of a length and outside off, McCullum pushes to Hussey at cover point
helf volley on middle and Guptill plays the perfect on drive, just to the right of the stumps and it races away for four. Gorgeous stroke
better length this time and Guptill drives but misses, beaten by the angle across him it seems
full again and Guptill drives nicely to mid off
this one decks away slightly from Guptill and he plays and misses outside off, well bowled
good length just on or outside off and he punches to Hussey at point off the back foot
half volley outside off and Guptill hits beautifully through the line for four past the man at short cover
half volley on off stump to get underway and McCullum drives straight to mid off for a single
full outside off and it takes the outside half of the bat and runs to third man
slightly slower this time and it's back of a length and McCullum works it off his hip
good channel and Guptill defends into the off side
good length again attacking the stumps and Guptill pushes strongly to point
Johnson continues to hit a nice channel and he hurries Guptill up as he defends to point off the outside edge
Bollinger is around the wicket and has McCullum defending back down the pitch

good length, McCullum moves back and looks to push into the off side, it takes the inside edge back onto his pads and then onto the stumps and Bollinger is rapt with that. Well bowled, the change of angle did the trick
good length but a fraction too straight and Taylor plays to square leg
Bollinger hustles in and attacks the body and Taylor defends off the back foot to square leg
good channel from Bollinger and Taylor allows it through to Haddin
fuller on off stump and Taylor drives powerfully into the ground and White gets a hand to it at short cover
full and just outside off stump and he drives nicely but straight to Hussey at point
back of a length and Guptill goes back and plays late, guiding it to third man
good length from Johnson draws Taylor forward and he defends strongly into the off side
pace and bounce from Johnson and Taylor is back and jumping into a defensive shot and the ball falls into the point region safely
decent length but wide and Taylor stands tall and square drives through point for four, super stroke to get underway
slower ball along the same line and Taylor spots the chane of pace and allows it through to the keeper
cracking length from Bollinger forces Guptill back and it takes an inside edge, straight into the ground and it bounces over the stumps
decent length angled across Guptill and he drives beautifully through extra cover for four, great timing
around the wicket now and he's full again and Guptill drives to mid off
great delivery from Bollinger forces Guptill back and he fends it away from his body, it takes the outside of the bat and runs to third man
back over the wicket and Taylor drives a full delivery to mid off
good channel and Taylor allows it through to the keeper
fuller on leg stump and Guptill pushes to mid on
full and a hint of shape back into Guptill, it takes him on the pad and the bowler goes up in appeal but it's going down leg
back of a length and pushed to point off the outside half of the bat
fuller, a fraction slower and Guptill drives from low on the bat in the air to White at short cover who takes a very easy catch, well bowled Johnson and the Australians are delighted
Johnson shapes it back into Broom just slightly and he gets an inside edge onto his pads
back of a length and Broom pushes into the off side
superb delivery from Harris beats Taylor outside off. Taylor looks at the pitch as though that moved a fraction
back of a length and Taylor plays early trying to work it through square leg and it falls into the leg side off the edge
full and pushed into the off side
Harris continues to demand a lot of the batsmen, hitting a great length and Taylor defends to extra cover
back of a length at middle stump and Taylor plays to mid wicket
finally Harris misses his channel and it's short and wide and Taylor cuts just over the top of point for four
back of a length and Broom defends square of the wicket on the off side
bumper from Johnson but well down the leg side
good length and slightly slower from Johnson and Broom plays to point where Hussey dives to field nicely
back into the pads and Broom clips it off his hip to fine leg
fullish outside off and Taylor drives strongly to the off side sweeper
good length and Broom comes forward and uses the pace, guiding it through backward point and Bollinger dives on the boundary to save the boundary and they take two
too straight and Broom is easily able to whip it backward of square on the leg side to the sweeper
cracking yorker from Harris and Broom digs it out
good channel and Broom drives off the outside edge through where first slip would've been and Haddin isn't able to move to get anywhere near it and it runs away for four
four more to Broom and Harris strays in line and Broom clips it fine past fine leg for four
angled into leg stump and Broom works it to mid wicket
good yorker again from Harris and Broom plays it into the leg side
good length attacking off stump and Broom defends back to Harris who shapes to throw the keepers' stumps down but holds back
Hauritz gives it air to start with and Taylor goes down on one knee early, it dips on him but he sweeps it fine of deep square leg for four
swept from well outside off to deep mid wicket with no timing
tossed up and Broom defends off the inside edge
flighted again and Broom plays it later this time and times it nicely to cover
flatter and in at the pads and Broom works into the leg side for an easy single
tossed up again but straighter this time and Taylor whips it through square leg to the sweeper
full and square driven off the outside half to third man
good length and Broom mistimes the drive into the off side
full and Broom drives strongly to short cover. Hopes really hustling through his overs here
half volley on off stump and Broom crunches it but straight to mid off
good length but too straight and Broom works it off his hip
full outside off and Taylor drives to White at extra cover who dives to field the ball cleanly
nicely flighted from Hauritz and Broom is beaten on the inside edge and Haddin can't hold on and they take a bye. That has turned a mile from outside off
well flighted and Taylor drives through mid off
slightly flatter and Broom cuts to backward point
tossed up and Broom uses his feet and plays back to the bowler
full outside off and Broom waits for it and drives through mid on for a single
nicely flighted and Taylor plays nicely into the leg side and the pair run a quick couple to square leg
comes down the track and cuts to point
good length and Broom is half forward and playing to third man
back of a length and wide down the leg side
angled into the pads and Taylor collects to fine leg off his hip
good delivery but Broom drives nicely back past Hopes for a single to mid off
good delivery and Taylor pushes into the off side
god length again and Taylor plays with softer hands and gaps it nicely to get a quick single
tossed up outside off and Taylor uses the pace to play through backward point to the sweeper
well flighted and Broom tries to sweep but misses
nicely flighted again and Broom moves across to the line outside off and works it through mid on
straighter to Taylor and he plays through square leg
arm ball from Hauritz and there's some encouraging drift but it's outside the wide line, Broom looks to cut but misses
tossed up and Broom defends into the off side for a well run single
tossed up nicely again and Taylor pushes with soft hands into the off side for another single
yorker and Taylor places it nicely into the covers, it beats White and they get two to the sweeper
full outside off and driven sweetly to White at cover
angled into the leg stump and Taylor works it through the leg side for a couple to long leg
good length and Taylor plays with soft hands into the off side for a quick single
angled down leg again and Broom whips it fine to fine leg
short outside off and Taylor pulls powerfully over square leg for six. Hussey dives full stretch in the deep and can't get a finger on it as it bounces just over the rope
full and Broom pushes forward and plays into the off side
full and slow outside off, Taylor tries to sweep it fine but misses
Taylor shapes to come down the track but sees it is short and cuts to backward point
tossed up again wide of off stump and Taylor goes down on one knee and slog sweeps over long on for six
full again and Taylor is forced to wait for this one and he square drives forward of point in the gap
flatter and Broom goes to cut but misses
full and wide of off and square driven to third man
back of a length and Broom uses the pace and guides to third man
half volley and Taylor drives nicely through the off side to Harris the sweeper who slides to save the boundary and they take a couple
full and pushed to mid off for a quick single
good length and Broom comes forward and pushes into the off side into the gap at point for one
Hopes attacks the stumps with a slightly slower delivery and Taylor gets a leading edge along the ground into the off side
Johnson back into the attack much to the angst of the crowd. He hits a good channel and Broom defends into the off side
too straight and Broom gets inside the line and works it into the off side
shorter this time and Taylor plays with soft hands into the off side
full and driven to cover
half volley and a hint of away swing and Broom drives off the outside half of the bat to point

cracking ball from Johnson as he spears it into leg stump, it swings away just enough and Broom is squared up trying to play to mid on/mid wicket and it takes the edge through to Watson at first slip. Australia and Johnson break what was a promising partnership
full and just enough width for Taylor to square drive past point for four. Great half century from Taylor
full and driven nicely to mid off
good length but Taylor plays with soft hands into the off side for a short single
back of a length and Styris is back and across and driving back to the bowler
good length and he hurries Styris up and he pushes back to the bowler
bumper from Hopes, Styris shapes to pull but then decides against it as it's a little quicker than he originally thought
full and wide half volley which beats Taylor on the outside of the bat, hint of away swing to the right hander
back of a length and Taylor moves back and looks to push into the off side, it takes the inside edge and rolls into the leg side and they have time for a single
full and some more away swing from the right handed Styris and he is beaten on the drive
back of a length and Styris works it to mid wicket
back of a length again and cut to point
full and wide and square driven to deep point, well timed but straight to the man on the fence
short and cut straight to point
shortish and cut again but off the top edge fine down to third man and Hauitz does really well down there to keep the scoring to two
full on off stump and Taylor pushes into the off side
good length on off again and he defends back to the bowler
good length and Taylor moves forward and pushes into the off side through the gap at point
back of a length and Styris drives on the up back to the bowler
good length and Taylor plays back to the bowler
good length again and Taylor plays later this time and into the off side for a quick single
tossed up outside off and Styris leaves
flatter this time and he guides to short third man
well flighted and this one really turns, hitting Johnson's footmarks and it takes Styrius on the pads as he looks to play into the off side
Styris plays a pre-meditated sweep and misses outside off stump, well bowled by Hauritz
slower ball and Taylor defends into the off side
good length and driven off the outside half of the bat to point who moves well to save one
fuller outside off and pushed to cover for one
good length and Styris moves back and drives back to the bowler
slower ball, leg cutter, angled into leg stump and Styris plays to mid wicket
back of a length at middle stump, Styris is back and pushing to long on from the back foot, good cricket
nicely flighted outside off and full and Styris drives to long on
good length and Taylor plays with soft hands to backward point and they take a quick single as the ball hits Taylor in thr back from the throw at the stumps
full and straight and worked into the leg side
full and straight again and Taylor whips it through the leg side
wide of off stump again and Styris works it from well outside off through backward square on the leg side
too straight and whipped into the leg side again
back of a length and defended into the off side

bumper from Watson and Taylor takes the bait, pulling off the top edge out to Hussey on the square leg fence, he moves forward and takes the catch low down. Watson has a real knack of taking wickets at crucial times and there's another. Advantage Australia. Taylor absolutely furious with himself
back of a length and Styris defends into the off side
good length again and Styris pushes into the off side
back of a length and too straight and Styris whips it through the leg side
good length has Hopkins fending into the point region
outside off stump and he plays into the off side
good length and Styris plays aerially towards mid on
good length and Styris works it past Ponting at mid wicket and they complete two
super shot from Styris as Hopes offers just a fraction of width and Styris square drives backward of point for four, great timing
attacks the stumps and played into the leg side
good length and defended back along the pitch to the bowler
good channel to Hopkins and he's in behind it defending back to the bowler
back of a length and Hopkins pushes into the off side but can't find a gap
short from Watson and Hopkins moves inside the line and it's called wide down leg
Watson continues to ask questions, attacking the stumps and Hopkins pushes back along the pitch
slower ball brings Hopkins forward and he plays to point, calls yes, but Styris says no straight away
good length hurries Hopkins up and he pushes towards mid on for a single
fuller on middle stump and Styris drives comfortably to long on
full outside off and Styris drives nicely through the off side to Hussey on the boundary and they have plenty of time to collect a couple
good length on off stump and he uses the pace and guides to third man
Hopkins comes forward and plays into the off side
fuller this time and Hopkins drives through the gap at point to the sweeper on the off side
short and Styris pulls it fine for a single
back of a length outside off and Hopkins plays neatly into the gap at point
wide of off stump and Hopkins guides it fine to third man

good length and Styris moves back and punches through straight mid wicket off the back foot, Bollinger chases it down and flicks it back inside the rope but nobody is following him to collect. He hits the picket fence and stays down. Menawhile the batsmen run four. Bollinger stays down and the medical staff come on to assess him and the umpires decide to take drinks
angled into the pads and Styris clips it through square leg
yorker played nicely to mid wicket
good channel and Hopkins plays and misses just outside off
angled into the pads and Hopkins chips it through mid wicket for a couple to Hussey who moves around nicely from square leg on the fence to collect
fullish and Styris square drives through point to the sweeper
good channel and Hopkins pushes into the off side with his bottom hand
outside off stump and Styris tries to play to long on but mistimes it to mid wicket
angled into leg stump and Styris clips it fine to fine leg
great channel again and Hopkins is beaten outside off stump
a fraction fuller and Hopkins hammers it between the two men inside the circle at point for four. Great gapping from the wee man
good length angled across Styris and he uses the pace to play to third man
around the wicket to Hopkins and he gets an inside edge to the sweeper at square leg
good length and Styris plays as late as possible with soft hands and drops the ball just beside the stumps allowing for a very comfortable single, well played
Hopkins moves across to off stump and tries to defend into the leg side, it takes him low on the torso and it runs towards third man
angled into Styris' hip and he clips it to deep square leg
bumper from Bollinger and Hopkins goes underneath and tries to ramp it but misses
tossed up and worked to Ponting at mid wicket
short outside off and Styris cuts to deep point
short again outside off and Hopkins drives through point to the sweeper
fuller and straighter and Styris works it through square leg for a single
well flighted outside off and Hopkins comes forward and tries to play into the off side but misses and Haddin takes the bails off but he never left the crease
tossed up outside off and Hopkins moves across his stumps and plays through square leg
good channel played to point
Hopkins comes forward and plays off the inside edge to White at mid wicket
fuller on off stump and Hopkins tries to whip it straight through the leg side but hits it to White again at mid wicket
good bouncer from Bollinger forces Hopkins to go underneath as he looks to ramp but pulls out
back of a length and Hopkins comes forward and uses the pace, playing to Voges at point but he misfields to allow a single
good length and Styris tries to drive, gets an inside edge back onto his pad and then in the air towards the bowler but it falls well short and there's no run
nicely flighted outside off and Hopkins tries to sweep but can't get enough on it
Hopkins walks across his stumps and whips it through the leg side
Styris moves across to the off side and works it behind square on the leg side with soft hands
played straight to mid wicket from outside off
short and wide and cut to deep point
tossed up on off stump and Styris drives nicely to long on. New Zealand content on taking the singles as they work towards the batting power play... when will they take it?
short delivery cramps Styris for room on the pull and it goes in the air towards mid wicket but wide of White and they get a single
full and clipped to mid wicket from just outside off stump
Bollinger goes short and Hopkins upper cuts over third man for six. Daryl Tuffey, who is not playing due to a calf strain, stands up off his seat and takes a comfortable catch in the stands
angled into the hip and he collects into the leg side
full on off stump and Styris waits for it and drives through point to the sweeper
short and cut to point, Voges dives to save it but can't hold onto it and they get a single
full and pushed into the off side for a single
short and Styris sways inside the line
fullish length and Styris pushes to Hauritz at mid on and he steals a sharp single, well run
full and Hopkins drives off the inside edge onto his foot and into the off side for a quick single
back of a length and Styris moves back and defends with soft hands into the off side for another short single
around the wicket and full, Hopkins square drives to the point sweeper, well timed but he couldn't find a bigger gap in the deep
half volley driven to cover
short and cut over point to the sweeper on the bounce, well timed but he couldn't pick the gap in the deep
back of a length but just a fraction too straight and Styris whips him over backward square for a maximum. Great timing
better length and played into the off side
fuller from Watson, Styris tires to hit him straight down the ground over the top, he plays too early and gets it high in the air and Harris moves forward from long off to take the catch at mid off
fuller again and driven to mid off
short ball from Johnson, Vettori tries to ramp it but misses

Vettori moves back and pushes into the off side and sets off for a run, taking on Ponting at cover, Ponting picks it up and hits the stumps to find Vettori just short of his ground, superb fielding from the skipper!
full outside off and driven to cover
full and too wide of off stump
back of a length and worked off his hip to short fine leg
150 kph, good length outside off, Hopkins tries to drive through the off side but misses
good length on middle and played into the on side
good bouncer and Bond ducks underneath
back of a length at the body and Bond plays back along the pitch
full on off stump and driven firmly to mid off
good length and Hopkins punches on the up over cover for four. That's a difficult stroke to play but he made it look quite easy
Hopkins goes inside the line and helps it on it's way over short fine leg for four
yorker speared into off stump and Hopkins digs it out to mid on for a single
Hopkins goes deep in the crease and pulls off the top edge over fine leg for six. Crucial runs for New Zealand and Hopkins playing a very handy role at the death here
fuller and driven to long on
good length on middle stump and Bond tries to swing it over the leg side, it takes a leading edge over square third man for six!
bumper down the leg side and the crowd roars
in the slot outside off and Bond swings and misses
half volley crunched to mid off
Dropped Bond swings it high in the air over mid off, Hopes moves back and puts it down and they take two. It just seems as though he took his eye off it at the crucial moment

low full toss and Hopkins drives in the air to Watson at mid off. He got underneath it but got it high on the blade with no timing whatsoever. Important breakthrough for Australia with only Southee and Mason to come
low full toss driven to point
edged to Haddin and he dives to his right one handed and yorks himself and can't hold onto it
good length driven to point again for another single

Southee walks slightly across his stumps and tries to work it through the leg side and it sneaks past his pads and takes leg stump and New Zealand sink further into trouble! Harris with another breakthrough
full on leg stick and clipped to long leg for a couple
outswinging yorker and Bond plays and misses just outside off
full and straight and Bond drives and edges through to Haddin and Australia wrap up the innings quickly.

inn2.comm: cracking start from Bond as this one hoops back into Watson from well outside off and he leaves it and it takes him high on the pads. New Zealand appeal but Bowden says not out
short from Bond and Watson pulls strongly through forward square leg for four
big inswinger again from Bond and it's fuller, takes Watson on the pad first then bat, they appeal and it's given not out
back of a length and Watson is in behind it and defending into the off side
fraction short and Watson is into position quickly and pulling powerfully over mid on for one bounce four, super shot!
fullish and wide of off and Watson leaves it alone
good length and Haddin is in behind it defending into the off side
angles down leg looking for too much swing and it's called wide
comes down the pitch and drives on the up to Vettori at mid off on the bounce
back of a length and defended into the off side
Haddin walks away to leg and launches it in the air towards Vettori at mid off again but it falls short
short and wide and cut backward of point for a couple. Ingram does well on the fence to save the boundary
good length and Haddin is back and defending into the off side just beside the stumps
fuller and wider from Bond and Watson allows it through to the keeper
full and wide again and Watson is down on one knee and driving nicely but straight to Guptill at cover
half volley on off stump and Watson drives sweetly to mid off where Vettori does well to pick it up
good length and Watson uses the width to guide to Taylor at first slip
back of a length and wider of off this time and Watson guides it nicely to third man
good length delivery outside off and Haddin moves across and defends into the off side, playing well away from his body but he played it late and watched it hard enough
good length from Southee forces Watson back and into a defence
Southee attacks the stumps and Watson plays to mid wicket
good channel and Watson uses the width to guide it to third man
Southee angles into the pads and Haddin clips it to the left of Bond at short fine leg and they take an easy single
back of a length and Watson plays into the off side
full on middle stump and Watson drives neatly to mid on
full on off stump and Haddin drives in the air to Vettori at mid off on the bounce
good length on off stump and defended into the off side
back of a length wide outside off and Haddin punches to point off the back foot
fuller and we see a hint of inswing and Haddin drives to Vettori at mid off
half volley on or outside off stump and Haddin drives to Styris at cover
absolute jaffa from Bond and Haddin is committed to play the line, back of a length, it nips away a fraction and it just slides past the outside edge
good length on off stump and Watson is in behind it and defending into the off side
short and wide from Southee, Watson winds up and cracks through backward point for four
back to a good length and Watson is forced to defend off the back foot
fraction fuller from Southee and Watson defends off the front foot into the off side
Southee bends his back and it's just short enough for Watson to pull off the bottom edge to McCullum at deep square leg
back of a length and enough width for Haddin to cut to third man
Bind hones in on off stump and Haddin plays into the off side
full and too straight from Bond and Haddin clips it through mid wicket for four, great shot

Dropped Bond charges in and goes fuller to Haddin who drives it straight back at him in the air and he can't hold onto it in his follow through. Bond's left hand has blown up remarkably in just a short time and he is receiving some attention from the medical staff
much slower this time from Bond as it's back of a length and Haddin drives off the back foot to point
fuller and driven off the outside half of the bat to McCullum at point and he parries it and they take a quick single
hits a good channel again and Watson plays into the off side

Southee bends his back and Haddin is forward and it takes the outside edge, Hopkins runs around to pick up while Watson has called him through for the single and Hopkins hits the stumps to find Watson short of his ground. Great work from the wee fella behind the stumps
good length outside off and Ponting allows it through to the keeper
back of a length and Ponting gets an inside edge past his stumps to fine leg to get underway
good length and played into the off side
slower ball and worked into the leg side through mid wicket for a single to the leg side sweeper
cracking ball from Southee as he really hits the deck, hits a good length and Ponting comes forward and tries to drive on the up but it beats the outside edge and through to Hopkins
half volley just outside off and Haddin drives straight back past the bowler for four, superb timing
good length and Haddin stands on the crease and plays into the off side
full slower ball from Bond and Haddin plays too early and mistimes/drags it into the pitch and back to the bowler
back of a length but too straight allows Haddin to whip it into the leg side for a comfortable single
good length on off stump and Ponting plays back down the line and to the bowler
full and wide and pushed to McCullum at point
back of a length in at the body and Haddin gets an inside edge into the leg side and they're able to complete two
good length and Haddin punches the ball into the off side
decent length again and Haddin tries to heave it over the leg side and doesn't time it and it rolls to Mason at mid on
good length and Haddin works it into mid wicket for a single
Southee continues to hit the deck and Ponting is back and defending into the covers

Dropped Ponting tries to drive Southee on the up, it takes a thick edge and Taylor dives full stretch to his right at first slip, he gets a couple of fingers to it and races away for four. Good effort from Taylor to get close to that
good channel from Mason and with no slip Haddin guides it fine for four, well played. He has overstepped as well! Free-hit coming up
Haddin sits back in his crease and launches a full delivery over long on for six! Super stroke
full on middle stump and Haddin flicks it through mid wicket for four
full and driven back to the bowler
decent length from Mason and Haddin drives on the up, just to the left of Mason's outstretched hand and it runs away for four
better length and Haddin can only play into the off side
full on middle and Haddin drives beautifully back past the bowler for a single to long off
too straight from Southee and Haddin gets a pad on it and they take a leg bye into the leg side
back of a length and Ponting waits nicely on it and punches through point for four, that is a classy shot
draws Ponting forward and he guides to third man off an open face
shortish and wide and Haddin cuts off the bottom edge through to Hopkins on the bounce
short and wide and cut to third man
fuller and attacking off stump and Ponting is forward and defending with hard hands into the off side
slower ball driven to long off
good length on off stump and Ponting gets an inside edge onto his pads and feels a little pain
back of a length and Ponting plays into the off side
good channel again and Ponting drives firmly to mid off
slower ball drifts down leg and Ponting hits it out of the middle and it beats the men behind square on the leg side for four
fuller and driven to mid on
flat on middle and Haddin plays to mid on and steals a quick single
good delivery from Vettori has Ponting defending from the crease
well flighted and Ponting comes forward and plays back to the bowler
tossed up on off stump and Ponting lunges forward and defends into the off side
arm ball from Vettori drifts into leg stick and Ponting clips him into the leg side
nicely flighted and drifted towards leg stump and he plays through mid wicket to the sweeper
good length from Mason but Haddin has no respect, driving on the up over long on for six! Immense timing
fullish and driven sweetly to Styris at short cover
he attacks middle stump this time and Haddin heaves it through the leg side to the sweeper
fuller and punched to Styris at mid off who does well to restrict the scoring to one
